{{#partial "content"}}

<p>Obtain
GitHub <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/github/authenticating-to-github/creating-a-personal-access-token">personal access token</a>
and use it as a password in authentication through package managers,
your username is <code>github.com/{{user}}</code>.</p>

